parameters: "I'm starving... Why won't the rice grow, why..."\n<Male Ghost>

"The rice has... grown... With this, everyone will be spared
from hunger. Thank goodness, thank goodness... The village
will be saved..."\n<Male Ghost>

(The rice plants are swaying. But they're completely
withered.)

(This withered rice... if I water it and pour some of the
god of fertility's spirit into it, it might revive. I should
go to the well and draw some water.)\F[4]

"Heave-ho, heave-ho... I've managed to grow rice before, but
this is my first time harvesting it."\n<Yukine>\F[12]
After some time, they finished harvesting the rice.
"This should be enough. Let's go give it to that ghost."\n<Yukine>\F[1]

(There's water in the well. Maybe I should give some to the
rice plants.)\F[1]
"Then... I'll infuse this with my divine energy..."\n<Yukine>

When the power of fertility was infused, the withered rice
plants bore many rice ears.

"It's been a while since I used my divine energy, but it
seems to have worked well. We might be able to harvest soon.
Did we have any tools for harvesting?"\n<Yukine>

(Hmm... there are signs that this stone has been turned
over. I can't lift it, but maybe I can tilt it.)\F[5]
"No, it's nothing. Sorry for worrying you."\n<Yukine>\F[7]\AA[F]\FF[24]

(This... It's a sickle for harvesting. It still seems
usable.)\F[1]
"It's an edible wild plant. Let's take this with us."\n<Yukine>\F[1]\AA[F]\FF[22]
"It's an edible mushroom. Let's take a few with us."\n<Yukine>\F[1]\AA[F]\FF[22]

(Saku's eyes may not have healed, but thank goodness she was
spared from witnessing such a cruel scene.)\F[7]

(The dolls have gathered and she's become able to speak
well, and her complexion is slowly getting better.)\F[1]

(If we can completely gather the dolls, maybe we can bring
Saku's spirit back to life.)\F[2]

"It's nothing. Let's go on to the next place. Are you tired,
Saku?"\n<Yukine>\F[1]\AA[F]\FF[22]
"I'm fine. But, I want to hold hands."\n<Saku>\F[1]\AA[FF]\FF[40]
